  "governance_notes": "All children are stateless (no global_vars). Data operations are limited to builds store only. ParseInput and FormatOutput are pure functions with no data store access. CheckExistingBuild, CheckBuildStatus, and ListBuilds require read capability on builds store. TriggerBuild and CancelBuild require write capability on builds store. Constraints ensure input validation, output formatting, and proper state transitions."
